author: Peter Spence
title: Stong rise in US jobs puts Federal Reserve on track for September rate hike
text: Stong rise in US jobs puts Federal Reserve on track for September rate hike The US Fed could raise its interest rates as soon as September Job gains in excess of 200,000 in July and August would prompt a September hike Photo: AP By Peter Spence , Economics Correspondent 2:16PM BST 07 Aug 2015
